  "short_description": "A 2d6 dice narrative adventure game book. Play as an acolyte of the Gilded Order. Venture out on quests with the Spellbook of Sky under the guise of the Ancients. Death and folly reign in this world of Dungeons and Dragons, where the realm is torn under warring clans you'll come to discover.",
