  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The debut game book by Kudomos; an epic adventure of sorcery!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3647380/extras/23807f1085df91c442a4163c04ca524d.poster.avif?t=1747883890\" width=800 height=454 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3647380/extras/23807f1085df91c442a4163c04ca524d.webm?t=1747883890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3647380/extras/23807f1085df91c442a4163c04ca524d.mp4?t=1747883890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Playing as a Gilded Sky acolyte, and issued a quest upon graduation from the Sky Guild, you'll navigate the high fantasy landscape steeped in dungeons and dragons lore. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this 2d6 dice narrative adventure game book, you face up to skill, luck or stamina challenges with the roll of the die: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3647380/extras/c04d4a6b0b1e6083a825d83e0a14371b.poster.avif?t=1747883890\" width=780 height=414 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3647380/extras/c04d4a6b0b1e6083a825d83e0a14371b.webm?t=1747883890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3647380/extras/c04d4a6b0b1e6083a825d83e0a14371b.mp4?t=1747883890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find creatures and puzzles along the way, as you are presented with the ever expansive quest of the Ancients. In a self-motivated journey the avatar must decide on not only their own fate, but that of the entire realm in this story rich, & choice rich adventure featuring over 40 unique and gory deaths should you choose unwisely.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The debut game book by Kudomos; an epic adventure of sorcery!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3647380/extras/23807f1085df91c442a4163c04ca524d.poster.avif?t=1747883890\" width=800 height=454 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3647380/extras/23807f1085df91c442a4163c04ca524d.webm?t=1747883890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3647380/extras/23807f1085df91c442a4163c04ca524d.mp4?t=1747883890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Playing as a Gilded Sky acolyte, and issued a quest upon graduation from the Sky Guild, you'll navigate the high fantasy landscape steeped in dungeons and dragons lore. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this 2d6 dice narrative adventure game book, you face up to skill, luck or stamina challenges with the roll of the die: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3647380/extras/c04d4a6b0b1e6083a825d83e0a14371b.poster.avif?t=1747883890\" width=780 height=414 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3647380/extras/c04d4a6b0b1e6083a825d83e0a14371b.webm?t=1747883890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3647380/extras/c04d4a6b0b1e6083a825d83e0a14371b.mp4?t=1747883890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find creatures and puzzles along the way, as you are presented with the ever expansive quest of the Ancients. In a self-motivated journey the avatar must decide on not only their own fate, but that of the entire realm in this story rich, & choice rich adventure featuring over 40 unique and gory deaths should you choose unwisely.</p>",
